    "Filters":{"extractionState":"manual","localizations":{"en":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Filters"}},"ar":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"عوامل التصفية"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"筛选条件"}},"de":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Filter"}},"hi":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"फ़िल्टर"}},"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"フィルタ"}},"ru":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Фильтры"}},"es-MX":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Filtros"}},"es-ES":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Filtros"}}}},
    "Flashcards Open Source App can send study reminders with a card from your review queue. These notifications contain study cards only and never marketing messages.":{"extractionState":"manual","localizations":{"en":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Flashcards Open Source App can send study reminders with a card from your review queue. These notifications contain study cards only and never marketing messages."}},"ar":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"يمكن لتطبيق Flashcards Open Source App إرسال تذكيرات بالدراسة مع بطاقة من قائمة المراجعة لديك. تحتوي هذه الإشعارات على بطاقات دراسية فقط ولا تتضمن رسائل تسويقية مطلقًا."}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Flashcards Open Source App 可以从你的复习队列中选取卡片向你发送学习提醒。这些通知仅包含学习卡片，绝不会包含营销消息。"}},"de":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Flashcards Open Source App kann dir Lern-Erinnerungen mit einer Karte aus deiner Wiederholungswarteschlange senden. Diese Benachrichtigungen enthalten nur Lernkarten und niemals Marketingnachrichten."}},"hi":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Flashcards Open Source App आपकी समीक्षा कतार से एक कार्ड के साथ अध्ययन रिमाइंडर भेज सकता है। इन सूचनाओं में केवल अध्ययन कार्ड होते हैं, कभी भी मार्केटिंग संदेश नहीं।"}},"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Flashcards Open Source App は、復習キューのカードを使った学習リマインダーを送信できます。これらの通知には学習カードのみが含まれ、マーケティングメッセージは含まれません。"}},"ru":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Flashcards Open Source App может отправлять напоминания об учебе с карточкой из вашей очереди повторения. Эти уведомления содержат только учебные карточки и никогда не содержат маркетинговых сообщений."}},"es-MX":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Flashcards Open Source App puede enviarte recordatorios de estudio con una tarjeta de tu cola de repaso. Estas notificaciones solo contienen tarjetas de estudio y nunca mensajes promocionales."}},"es-ES":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Flashcards Open Source App puede enviarte recordatorios de estudio con una tarjeta de tu cola de repaso. Estas notificaciones solo contienen tarjetas de estudio y nunca mensajes promocionales."}}}},
    "Front":{"extractionState":"manual","localizations":{"en":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Front"}},"ar":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"الوجه الأمامي"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"正面"}},"de":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Vorderseite"}},"hi":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"सामने"}},"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"表面"}},"ru":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Лицевая сторона"}},"es-MX":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Frente"}},"es-ES":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Anverso"}}}},
    "Good":{"extractionState":"manual","localizations":{"en":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Good"}},"ar":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"جيد"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"良好"}},"de":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Gut"}},"hi":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"अच्छा"}},"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"良い"}},"ru":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Хорошо"}},"es-MX":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Bien"}},"es-ES":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Bien"}}}},
    "Hard":{"extractionState":"manual","localizations":{"en":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Hard"}},"ar":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"صعب"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"困难"}},"de":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Schwer"}},"hi":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"कठिन"}},"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"難しい"}},"ru":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Трудно"}},"es-MX":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Difícil"}},"es-ES":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Difícil"}}}},
    "Hard is for difficult recall":{"extractionState":"manual","localizations":{"en":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Hard is for difficult recall"}},"ar":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"يُستخدم \"صعب\" عندما يكون التذكر صعبًا"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"“困难”用于回忆起来较吃力的情况"}},"de":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"\"Schwer\" ist für Fälle, in denen dir das Erinnern schwerfiel"}},"hi":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"\"कठिन\" उस स्थिति के लिए है जब याद करना मुश्किल हो"}},"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"「難しい」は思い出すのに苦労した場合に使います"}},"ru":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"«Трудно» — для случаев, когда вспоминать было трудно"}},"es-MX":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"\"Difícil\" es para cuando te costó recordar"}},"es-ES":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"\"Difícil\" es para cuando te costó recordar"}}}},
    "If you did not know the answer, choose \"Again\". \"Hard\" is only for answers you knew but it was difficult to recall.":{"extractionState":"manual","localizations":{"en":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"If you did not know the answer, choose \"Again\". \"Hard\" is only for answers you knew but it was difficult to recall."}},"ar":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"إذا لم تكن تعرف الإجابة، فاختر \"مرة أخرى\". يُستخدم \"صعب\" فقط للإجابات التي عرفتها لكن كان تذكرها صعبًا."}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"如果你不知道答案，请选择“重来”。“困难”仅适用于你知道答案但回忆起来很吃力的情况。"}},"de":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Wenn du die Antwort nicht wusstest, wähle \"Nochmal\". \"Schwer\" ist nur für Antworten gedacht, die du wusstest, aber nur schwer abrufen konntest."}},"hi":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"अगर आपको उत्तर नहीं पता था, तो \"फिर से\" चुनें। \"कठिन\" केवल उन उत्तरों के लिए है जिन्हें आप जानते थे, लेकिन याद करना मुश्किल था।"}},"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"答えがわからなかった場合は「もう一度」を選んでください。「難しい」は、答えは知っていたものの思い出すのに苦労した場合にのみ使います。"}},"ru":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Если вы не знали ответ, выберите «Снова». «Трудно» подходит только для ответов, которые вы знали, но их было трудно вспомнить."}},"es-MX":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Si no sabías la respuesta, elige \"Otra vez\". \"Difícil\" es solo para respuestas que sí sabías pero te costó recordarlas."}},"es-ES":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Si no sabías la respuesta, elige \"Otra vez\". \"Difícil\" es solo para respuestas que sí sabías pero te costó recordarla."}}}},
